snippet.title: I Wani Hug That Gator Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
I Wani Hug that Gator! is a choice-driven narrative about teenagers struggling to find their way.​

Here's the picture: You're Inco, a new human transfer student to St. Hammond High, where the curriculum is focused on the Arts. There you'll meet a number of colorful new friends such as the captivating baryonyx Olivia, along with other dinosaurs that are more vibrant than the canvases they paint on. As the only human in this Jurassic school, you'll have to consider your choices in order to thrive.

Download:
https://hugthegator.xyz
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1895350/I_Wani_Hug_that_Gator/
https://cavemanon.itch.io/i-wani-hug-that-gator-demo
